---
import Section from './Section.astro';
import { about } from '../data/content';
---
<Section id="about" title={about.title}>
  <div class="about-body">
    <p>
      I'm a Software Engineer living in <strong>Tokyo, Japan</strong> — building cloud-native systems at
      <strong>Denso</strong> by day, and quietly obsessing over clean architecture by night.
    </p>
    <p>
      My path here wasn't a straight line. I grew up in Jodhpur, India, earned a B.E. in Computer Science,
      then pushed harder for an M.Tech at <strong>IIT Hyderabad</strong> — one of the country's most
      competitive research institutions. That grind sharpened my instinct for digging deep into problems
      rather than just patching the surface.
    </p>
    <p>
      These days I live at the intersection of <strong>cloud infrastructure and full-stack development</strong>.
      I've designed IaC pipelines with Terraform, wired up observability stacks from scratch with Prometheus
      and Grafana, and shipped React + Node.js products that actually scale. I'm an
      <strong>AWS Certified Solutions Architect</strong> — not because a badge means everything, but because
      I wanted proof I could design systems that don't fall apart at 3 AM.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not staring at dashboards or debugging CI pipelines, I'm on a football pitch, at a
      table tennis table, or in the pool — sports that reward you for staying sharp and thinking fast,
      which is probably why I like them.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe the best engineers write code that their future selves won't hate, document the
      <em>why</em> not just the <em>what</em>, and treat on-call incidents as learning opportunities
      rather than disasters. Still working on that last one.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-body strong {
    color: var(--accent-4);
  }

  .about-body em {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about-body p { font-size: 0.97rem; }
  }
</style>
